 Installation
 ============

   Cheat comes with Commodore`s installer, therefor it`s quite easy to install
on your harddisk or disks. Just click twice on the install-icon in your
language.

Otherwise just copy Cheat to your desired place and copy your
language-catalogue into the LOCALE:xxx directory (xxx stands for your own
language).

@endnode

