@node "MSC_QUESTIONS" "Cheat.guide/MSC_QUESTIONS"
@next "MSC_HISTORY"
@prev "MSC_ACKS"


 Discussion
 ==========

Q:	I made an input in the searchvalue-gadget but `Cheat` is hunting for `0`. Why ?

A:	Just press `CR` or `Tab` to signal `Cheat` that you have changed the value.


Q:	Why does the `Trace-Mode` takes so long to deactivate ?
	Because of the seconds-gadget. `Cheat` is using this time to wait via Delay().
	Just decrease the value to shorten the time, but you will have a little bit more idle.


@endnode

